    Why Sponsor Us?

    Access Deep-Tech Talent

    Connect with 100+ high-potential student innovators and researchers working on science- and technology-driven ideas. Build early relationships with future founders and hires.

    Brand Visibility

    Showcase your brand through talks, booths, digital promotions, and on-ground event presence. Reach a focused academic and startup audience.

    Networking Opportunities

    Engage with student startups, faculty mentors, and innovation partners. Enable meaningful collaborations within the research-to-entrepreneurship ecosystem.

    Benefits :

    Data & Impact Insights

    Receive post-event reports including Audience demographics, Engagement metrics, Participation and outreach analytics

    Support Innovation & Education (CSR Impact)

    Contribute to strengthening Indias research-to-startup ecosystem by supporting student-led innovation and entrepreneurship.

    Sponsorship tiers

    Title Sponsor

    INR 10 lakhs

    Ideal for corporates and funding agencies seeking national visibility in research-driven entrepreneurship.
    Benefits :

    • Event co-branding as IIES 2026 Powered By .

    • Highest-priority logo placement across all platforms.

    • Opening and closing keynote opportunity.

    • Jury or mentor representation.

    • Sponsor-branded innovation challenge or award.

    • Premium stall at a prime venue location.

    • Full-page back-cover advertisement in the official brochure.

    • Up to 3 representatives may attend and present.

    • Detailed post-event impact and engagement report.

    Platinum Sponsor

    INR 5 lakhs

    Ideal for innovation-focused companies looking to showcase offerings and engage with student founders.
    Benefits :

    • Title recognition as Official Innovation Partner IIES 2026

    • Prominent logo placement on event materials and website.

    • 30-minute flagship talk or product demo session.

    • Dedicated premium booth or stall

    • Full-page advertisement in the official brochure.

    • Up to 2 representatives may attend and present.

    • Access to opt-in participant and audience insights

    • Post-event analytics and engagement report

    Gold Sponsor

    INR 2 lakhs

    Best suited for organizations seeking strong on-ground visibility and brand association with student innovation.
    Benefits :

    • High-visibility logo placement on event materials and website.

    • Dedicated booth or stall space.

    • Half-page advertisement in the official brochure.

    • Acknowledgement across major event communications.

    • One representative may attend and present.

    • Audience demographics and post-event report.

    Silver   Sponsor

    INR 1 lakhs

    Designed for startups and emerging companies seeking targeted visibility and engagement.
    Benefits :

    • Logo placement on website and official brochure

    • Recognition as a Session Sponsor

    • Dedicated booth or banner space

    • One representative may attend

    • Inclusion in post-event audience insights report

    Booth   Sponsor

    INR 50,000

    Ideal for lead generation, recruitment outreach, and product showcase.
    Benefits :

    • Dedicated booth with banner display

    • Logo placement on website and brochure

    • Participant lead collection opportunities

    • Mention on event map and social media

    Custom Sponsorship Options

    We offer flexible sponsorship partnerships, including in-kind and strategic collaborations such as:

    • Awards and prize sponsorships.

    • Student travel grants.

    • Merchandise and branding partnerships.

    Custom packages can be structured based on your goals and engagement needs.
